# Force LF line endings for everything in this repo, regardless of the
# user's global core.autocrlf setting. Shell scripts in particular break
# on CRLF: the shebang `#!/bin/bash\r` makes the loader fail, and every
# line read by bash gains a trailing \r that breaks quoting, comparisons,
# and heredoc terminators. JSON / MD are LF too for consistency.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
